   ├─ Telescope: 20cm diameter, off-axis
   ├─ Inertial reference: Fiber optic gyro (0.001°/hr)
   └─ Star tracker: 0.5 arcsec accuracy

2. Quantum source and detection
   ├─ Entangled photon source: 810nm & 1550nm
   ├─ Detectors: 4× SNSPD at 2.8K
   ├─ Quantum memory: Rubidium vapor cell
   └─ Classical beacon: 976nm, 1W for tracking

3. Ground segment
   ├─ 3 ground stations along flight path
   ├─ Each with adaptive optics
   ├─ Real-time telemetry and control
   └─ Data collection during overflights

Experiments:
