├─ Quantum detector: 4× SNSPD (same as Hawaii)
├─ Operations: ANU astronomers + quantum team
└─ Network: 100G to Sydney

Common Systems:
├─ Timing: Chip-scale atomic clocks (CSAC) synchronized to GPS
├─ Control software: Common codebase (Git repository)
